localhost:8080/api/dmi-dini/point

### persists a grid cell of the bbox from DMI Open Data
POST localhost:8080/api/dmi-dini-bbox/bbox-point

### returns a grid cell from our DB
localhost:8080/api/dmi-dini-bbox/bbox-point